name: Faux Shagreen Boutique Tissue Box Holder - Mole Brown
description: Our Faux Shagreen Boutique Tissue Box Holder transforms an everyday essential into beautiful décor for your home. An excellent addition to a bathroom or bedroom. Fits a square sized box of tissues. Veneered in our very realistic mole brown faux shagreen. Finished with a smart walnut trim. The tissue box holder simply slips over the top of the tissue box itself. Available in taupe.
